<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2919] Haxe test server timeout too large</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2919</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The timeout used to run the Thrift test server is too high. Because the process lives longer than intended, subsequent tests run by make check may be affected as the are not able to bind() the server socket as long as the previous server runs on the same port.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
